title: 2013 Jeep Wrangler 3.8 with Gibson Single Exhaust
description:
Part # 17301
12-15 Jeep Wrangler 3.6L Unlimited
07-11 Jeep Wrangler 3.8L

Jeep enthusiasts need power from idle to 3000 RPM, Gibson designed their jeep exhaust to enhance low and mid range power for climbing and towing. This single exhaust exits straight out the back, Complemented with polished Stainless Tip. Hassle free, bolt-on installation with professional looking results. Backed by a Lifetime Limited Warranty.

2.50-in. aluminized mandrel bent tubing.
Gibson Muffler features a baffled & chambered design, no internal packing, powerful deep tone.

– 4in. Polished T304 Stainless Rolled Slash- Cut Tip.
– Exit Is Straight Out The Back.
– Includes all hardware and factory style hangers for easy bolt on installation.
– Lifetime Limited Warranty
